body:
Adds some Radiohead-related stuff to the game. Currently it only changes paintings, however music disc changes are coming soon.
**WARNING: The Bends, A Moon Shaped Pool, OK Computer, and In Rainbows require commands to obtain. Here are those commands:**
- In Rainbows: /give @s painting{EntityTag:{variant:"water"}}
- The Bends: /give @s painting{EntityTag:{variant:"earth"}}
- A Moon Shaped Pool: /give @s painting{EntityTag:{variant:"wind"}}
- OK Computer: /give @s painting{EntityTag:{variant:"fire"}}
